Lambda expression can written for Function interfaces only
Functional Interface - an interface which contains only 1 abstract method

String name="geet";
double pi=3.14;
ablockofcode={statements;}

ablockofstatement= ()->	System.out.println("area of rectangle is L*B");

Shape s=new Shape(){
				public void draw() {
					// TODO Auto-generated method stub
					System.out.println("area of rectangle is L*B");
				}
			};

